Name: Microbox Core API
Description: The full API spec for Microbox Core, and other Nanobox-v1-compatible dashboard and coordination servers.

Endpoints.Name: registerHostingProvider
Endpoints.Description: Register a hosting provider adapter

Parameters.Name: token
Parameters.Description: the adapter registration token generated by the dashboard for this adapter

Endpoints.Name: unregisterHostingProvider
Endpoints.Description: Unregister a hosting provider adapter

Parameters.Name: token
Parameters.Description: the adapter registration token used to register this adapter

Parameters.Name: unlink_code
Parameters.Description: the unlink_code returned when this adapter was registered

EndpointGroups.Description: Endpoints for interacting with individual services within components.

EndpointGroups.Name: user
EndpointGroups.Description: Endpoints that interact with user data.
